{"word":"μοιχεύω","slug":"μοιχεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μοιχεύω</b></el> <el>(μοιχεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to commit adultery with</i> a woman, <i>to debauch</i> her, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, of the woman, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to commit adultery</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>moechari</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}